<abstract>
<p>Hill et al. claimed in previous work that sonic hedgehog signalling pathway is an essential regulator of astrocytes development. We present here a formalization of that claim, stating that all things of class “smoothened signaling pathway” that are in the context of a thing of class “human” mostly have a relation of type “affects” to a thing of class “astrocyte development” in the same context.</p>
</abstract>
